## CSS

- Use **OKLCH** for colors
- Use relative units (`rem`, `em`, `%`, `vw`, `vh`) — avoid `px` except for borders
- Use CSS logical properties: `margin-inline-start` not `margin-left`, `block-size` not `height`
- Use **cascade layers** in this order: `@layer config, resets, components, utilities`
- `@layer config` — CSS custom properties; `@layer resets` — resets; `@layer components` — component styles; `@layer utilities` — utility classes
- Prefixes: `c-` components, `u-` utilities, `js-` for JS selectors
- Use `:focus-visible` for focus states, not `:focus`
- Wrap transitions/animations in `@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference)`
- Use `text-transform` for uppercase; don't write all caps in markup
- No Tailwind; use [Autoprefixer](https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer) for vendor prefixes

